						<div class="postbody">...so what really prompted my thread was that the word &quot;Thread&quot; is present in the old Neotoxin source code. I also have heard at least one fellow homebrewer refer to things as &quot;threads&quot; in his code. I was just curious what these things actually were. Probably not &quot;real&quot; threads.</div>

